faq.a: You have to register for KYC / Whitelisting From and from the 1st of August you can buy tokens.

faq.q: Is KYC needed for bounty hunters?
faq.a: No. For Bounty Hunters KYC is not needed at the moment.

We are are developing a new blockchain for social security applications wich will be connected via bridges to other public blockchains like ethereum-blockchain, binnace-blockchain, polkadot-blockchain, etc.

faq.q: How can I buy ASR tokens?
faq.a:
The first to sign up for whitelisting.
From August 1th to August 15th there will be Smart Contract addresse on this website.
